data.description: Discover the charm of this stunning 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home in Mandarin! Featuring upgraded laminate wood flooring, granite countertops, and a luxurious master bathroom, this residence offers both style and comfort. Step inside to a spacious dining/living room combination and a cozy family room with a fireplace. Enjoy the tranquility of the screened-in patio overlooking fruit trees and a serene preserve, perfect for relaxation. The backyard provides ample shade and ultimate privacy, while the recently upgraded kitchen boasts granite countertops and plenty of dining space for gatherings. Retreat to the spacious primary bedroom, offering seclusion from the living area.
